description._content: Description: Troodos. Mature stand of Troodos Pine in Winter over 250 years old; Elevation 5751 ft. Location: Troodos, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Description: Troodos. Troodos Pine with natural reproduction underneath, 5760' elevation. Location: Troodos, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/697 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
